WEBVTT

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:35.376
The first sign of the impending cleansing

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.280
was the breakdown of trust
within communities.

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:42.936
Three days after I arrived in the country,

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:45.760
I watched the small city
of Gaga be abandoned.

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:49.280
A battle was about to break out.

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:51.936
And to save themselves,

00:01:51.960 --> 00:01:55.856
many people were working
as government spies,

00:01:55.880 --> 00:01:59.296
identifying friends and neighbors

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:00.520
to be killed.